      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh just landed in dubai after like 14 hours on a plane and my chest feels all sharp and weird whenever i try to take a deep breath. i feel kinda lightheaded too. i'm probably just super stressed from the travel anxiety right? i dont wanna go to a doctor if i can help it, maybe i should just try some breathing exercises or something?",
